General Information
===================

This is @PACKAGE@ version @VERSION@.  @PACKAGE@ allows users to
run and evaluate auditory models writing using simulation scripts.
It is in the form of a dynamic-linked library which is called directly
from Matlab/octave.
It is supported by the extensive collection of published and new models
supplied by the development system for auditory modelling (DSAM).

To use this application on UNIX the DSAM library must be installed.

The official web site is:

	http://www.dsam.org

A mailing list is located at: dsam@mailbase.ac.uk

To subscribe: visit the web site at:

	http://www.jiscmail.ac.uk/dsam

